- Go to the Spotify Developer Dashboard and log in.
- Create a new application.
- Set the Redirect URI to http://localhost:8888/callback in your app settings. Can change port (i.e. 8080, 8050, etc.,)
- Note down your Client ID and Client Secret.
- Update Spotify credentials:
  CLIENT_ID = "your_client_id_here"
  CLIENT_SECRET = "your_client_secret_here"
- The first time you run the app, a web browser for Spotify OAuth will open asking for permission.

   *Some API calls may require Spotify Premium.
